snippet.textDisplay: My foot ball team made me run a 10 minute mile in my stature in high school and I threw up trying so hard and for the ones who didn’t make it we had to run laps till midnight I told the coach to fuck off im here to hit people hard not run a marathon I also tried to run till midnight but I threw up again and I walked off because that was too intense for my big fat ass at that point I was 6’3’ 400 pounds I couldn’t run for shit I understand they were trying to push me and I hid the vomit the best I could but 11:00 rolled around and I couldn’t keep going me and another buddy of mine Kent 6’5 ‘350 not as much “muscle mass” as me because I would leg press like 800 lbs and enjoyed it because the pressure against my back made it pop off the cushion and I would do like 20 of them and if flabbergasted my friends so I kept doing it just to get an aw out of my buddies in PE then we went to the gym and I started maxing out all the pulley system weights maxed out like they were nothing in this cheap podunk towns club 24 . I punched my friend in the face because he didn’t think I could pull the whole rack with one arm I did and gave him the smallest chin tap ever but I did it and felt great I watched his head bearly snap back in disbelief as I did it and that look made me want to try even harder at the time now times have changed the end is coming and I can’t stop it only embrace the inevitable and indulge you the fans of unus annus to hear my story and do the best that you can to stay Healthy because one day it will be your last day and I hope it’s for all of the glory you have been waiting for, by the end of this I hope you at least get something out of this comment if you want to change it all start with you and taking the tinniest of steps such as just even walking around the track helps you may think it’s pointless and dumb but hey you can walk in a circle and still watch videos right??? So get off of your couch go out enjoy the day and you can keep watching but start working towards a better you got tomorrow today. “( in my deepest markiplier voice passable)”

(Jesus warning about HELL FIRE):


And if thy hand causes you to sin,
cut it off:


it is better for thee
to enter into life maimed,


than having two hands
to go into hell,
into the fire


that never shall be quenched:
Where their worm dieth not,
and the fire is not quenched.


(Mark 9:43-44).


***(Cut if off): Should be taken figuratively; it means to take whatever drastic action is necessary to avoid sin.


***The imagery of Hell (Frequently called gehenna) comes from a garbage dump outside the walls of Jerusalem. Jesus hearers were familiar with the smoldering fires that always burned there.


***(((Obedience))) and (((self-control))) are necessary to overcome sin.


***The longing of the disciples for greatness needed to be reshaped according to God's purposes.
